sequenceDiagram
    participant User as User Code<br/>(Notebook / Script)
    participant API as training-hub API<br/>sft() / osft() / lora_sft()<br/>lora_grpo() / grpo()
    participant Algo as Algorithm<br/>validate() + run()
    participant Backend as Backend<br/>train()
    participant Torchrun as torchrun<br/>(Subprocess)
    participant Framework as Training Framework<br/>(instructlab / mini-trainer<br/>/ Unsloth+TRL / ART / verl)
    participant vLLM as vLLM Engine<br/>(GRPO only)
    participant HFHub as HuggingFace Hub<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant Disk as Local Filesystem<br/>Checkpoints + Metrics

    Note over User,Disk: Flow 1: SFT / OSFT Training

    User->>API: sft(model_path, data_path,<br/>num_epochs, ...)
    API->>Algo: create_algorithm("sft", backend="instructlab")
    Algo->>Algo: validate() - type check params
    Algo->>Backend: run() → backend.train()
    Backend->>Torchrun: subprocess: torchrun<br/>--nproc_per_node=N
    Torchrun->>Framework: Execute training workers
    Framework->>HFHub: Download model/tokenizer<br/>Bearer: HF_TOKEN
    HFHub-->>Framework: Model artifacts
    Framework->>Disk: Save checkpoints + metrics.jsonl
    Framework-->>Torchrun: Training complete
    Torchrun-->>Backend: Exit code 0
    Backend-->>Algo: Return
    Algo-->>API: Return
    API-->>User: Training complete

    Note over User,Disk: Flow 2: LoRA GRPO Training (ART Backend - Single GPU)

    User->>API: lora_grpo(model, dataset,<br/>reward_funcs, ...)
    API->>Algo: create_algorithm("lora_grpo",<br/>backend="art")
    Algo->>Algo: validate() - check reward config
    Algo->>Backend: run() → backend.train()
    Backend->>vLLM: Start vLLM subprocess<br/>(rollout engine)
    Backend->>Backend: Create seed LoRA checkpoint<br/>(vLLM V1 compatibility)
    loop GRPO Training Loop
        Backend->>vLLM: POST prompts for generation<br/>HTTP (dynamic port)
        vLLM-->>Backend: Completions
        Backend->>Backend: Evaluate with reward function<br/>tool_call_reward / binary_reward
        Backend->>Backend: Compute GRPO policy gradient
        Backend->>Backend: Update LoRA adapter weights
    end
    Backend->>Disk: Save LoRA adapter checkpoint
    Backend->>vLLM: Shutdown vLLM subprocess
    Backend-->>User: Training complete

    Note over User,Disk: Flow 3: LoRA GRPO Training (verl Backend - Multi GPU)

    User->>API: grpo(model, dataset,<br/>backend="verl", ...)
    API->>Algo: create_algorithm("lora_grpo",<br/>backend="verl")
    Algo->>Backend: run() → backend.train()
    Backend->>Backend: Convert dataset to Parquet
    Backend->>Torchrun: subprocess: verl CLI<br/>with Hydra config overrides
    Torchrun->>Framework: Distribute across GPUs<br/>(NCCL / torch.distributed)
    Framework->>Disk: Save checkpoints
    Framework-->>Torchrun: Training complete
    Backend->>Backend: Post-process: merge tokenizer<br/>into adapter directories
    Backend-->>User: Training complete

    Note over User,Disk: Flow 4: GPU Memory Estimation

    User->>API: estimate(model_name,<br/>algorithm="sft", gpu_mem=80)
    API->>HFHub: GET model config<br/>HTTPS 443/TCP
    HFHub-->>API: Model metadata<br/>(param count, hidden size, ...)
    API->>API: Compute VRAM:<br/>model + gradients + optimizer<br/>+ activations + buffer
    API->>Disk: Cache model info (CSV)
    API-->>User: Estimated VRAM: 72.3 GB
